{"tid":2150683,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【蘋果25】這是最後一本報慶特刊嗎？走過25年《不是最終章》","createTime":"2020-08-11T05:00:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T13:34:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"9b93b6f17c6f577e82eb7aa9f0423bb77475d527","tid":2150683,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:00:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/XUEY7RQIIU4GJKI7FNX4L5AK54/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FXUEY7RQIIU4GJKI7FNX4L5AK54%2F&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lOu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=2b6ecc28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FXUEY7RQIIU4GJKI7FNX4L5AK54%2F&h=bb242b27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/XUEY7RQIIU4GJKI7FNX4L5AK54/</a><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》創刊10周年和20周年時，我們先後出版《回望香港十年》和《忘不了．20年》，20周年特刊的序言是這樣寫：「10年後，還會有30周年特刊嗎？風起了，惟有努力試着活下去。」今年，來到25周年，「港版國安法」兵臨城下，本來要多等5年的特刊，趕在亂世推出。各組同事總動員，參與編採、製作的，都抱着不一樣的心情。157頁的特刊，跨越四分一世紀，共分10個章節，有同事說，是懷着最後一次的心情去做。1995年6月20日，香港主權移交前，就像今天，人心躁動，移民潮爆發，外媒預言香港遲早「玩完」，《蘋果》偏偏在在這動盪時代誕生。25年來經歷時代變遷，目睹物換星移，見盡人心變向，《蘋果》在錯誤中成長，與港人同喜同悲。"},{"pid":"a6a7c7bb84f606c865988c3460d15f77cf41faaa","tid":2150683,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7480912eb4770b993670760a696523fd9167780c","tid":2150683,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:04:03.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass